- Describe a time when you had to handle multiple resposabilities at once.
    it's not in my resume, but I was in charge like a manager for two years.
    working in a control center in operation could be challenging, because most
    of the problems have to be solved in real time. It happened several time that we
    had to deliver analysis, reports, and solve the daily tasks at the same time. 
    My approach was to prioritize, delegate and set hours for each task.
  
